snippet.textDisplay: Awesome composition. The songs consist of a blend of current Uttarakhand pop music and classical Uttarakhand JAGAR (form of Shamanism). Neha Kakkar sang well; however, she lacks a Gharwali accent and feel. DigV justified his singing and showed his unique way of singing at last. Looking for more Uttrakhandi songs (especially Pandavas).
